sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    actor Ketua as Ketua Yayasan
    actor Penerima
    participant Halaman as Halaman Surat Masuk
    participant Controller as SuratMasukController
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Admin->>Halaman: Input data surat + pilih tujuan
    Halaman->>Controller: Simpan surat baru
    Controller->>DB: INSERT surat (status: DISPOSISI)
    Controller->>DB: INSERT disposisi ke Ketua
    DB-->>Controller: OK
    Controller-->>Halaman: Berhasil
    Controller-->>Ketua: Notifikasi surat baru
    Ketua->>Halaman: Buka detail surat
    Ketua->>Halaman: Disposisi ke Penerima
    Halaman->>Controller: Buat disposisi baru
    Controller->>DB: INSERT disposisi
    Penerima->>Halaman: Klik Selesai
    Halaman->>Controller: Selesaikan disposisi
    Controller->>DB: UPDATE status = SELESAI
